ori_content:
프리미엄 숯불닭구이 토리이에는
신선한 국내산 생닭을 고급 비장탄에 구워드시는 닭 숯불구이 전문점입니다
남녀노소 누구나 좋아하는 닭고기와 많이 접해보지 못하셨던 닭 특수부위를 트렌디한 공간 속에서
수제로만든 특제소스들을 곁들여 다양한 주류와 함께 즐겨보시길 바랍니다
tr_content: Toriie is a premium charcoal-grilled chicken restaurant, specializing in grilling fresh, domestically produced chicken on high-quality charcoal. This is a place that everyone, young and old, can enjoy. We serve popular chicken dishes and introduce lesser-known special parts of the chicken. In a trendy environment, we invite you to enjoy our homemade special sauces along with a wide range of alcoholic beverages.
Seafood and Soft Bean Curd Stew
rice mixed with pollack roe and egg
Kimchi, crab, chili powder from China
eggplant, green onion, spring onion, zucchini, cherry tomato, young corn)

ori_content:
소스는 황토소금, 카레가루, 청양유자소금, 불닭소스, 할라피뇨마요가 준비되어 있으며
황토소금과 카레가루, 청양유자소금은 앞접시에 조금씩 덜어 드시고
저희가 내어드리는 샐러드는 특제 샐러드소스에 넣어 고기와 함께 드시면 맛있게 드실 수 있습니다
저희 토리이에는 신선한 국내산 닭고기를 사용하고 있으며 익혔을때 붉은빛을 띌 수 있고
너무 많이 구워드시는 것보다 핏기만 없으면 바로 드시는걸 추천드립니다
tr_content: We have a variety of sauces prepared, including red clay salt, curry powder, Cheongyang Yuzu salt, spicy chicken sauce, and jalapeno mayo. The red clay salt, curry powder, and Cheongyang Yuzu salt can be spooned out in small amounts onto your plate. Our salad is best enjoyed when mixed with our special salad sauce and eaten with the meat. At Toriie, we use fresh, domestically produced chicken. It may take on a reddish color when cooked, and we recommend eating it as soon as it's cooked, as long as there is no blood left, rather than overcooking it.
